<p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">Subsec. (d). <ref href="/us/pl/110/417/s612/b">Pub. L. 110–417, § 612(b)</ref>, substituted “on or before <date date="2009-12-31">December 31, 2009</date>” for “before <date date="2009-01-01">January 1, 2009</date>”.</p>
